Beautiful beach - the China Beach of the Vietnam era
Nov 2019
I stopped here while in the Da Nang area. The beach is really beautiful and huge. The views from the beach looking out toward the water are also lovely. I had heard about this place, having grown up in the Vietnam era and was very pleased to be able to stop to see it and take a walk around.
