Jonathan C.
La Jolla, California, USA478 contributions
my khe beach
Feb 2023
Gorgeous beach in Da Nang. The sand is soft and fine, there are plenty of seashells, gentle waves for swimming and wading, lots of spots along the way for a drink or a beach chair under the shade. Lifeguards watch the swimming areas. Great views up and down the beach.
Written February 13, 2023
Caleb
Hillsboro, OR5 contributions
Sep 2022
Awesome beach. Very clean and nice beach. A lot of restaurant restaurants and hotels along the beach. My Khe beach is surrounded by fine white sand, temperate waves, year-round warm water. This has created the irresistible beauty of this beach.
